{"tid":903125,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【李卓人造勢大會】 日期｜11 月 16 日（星期五） 時間｜7.30-9.30PM 地點｜油麻地眾坊街榕樹頭公園","createTime":"2018-11-15T10:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T13:59:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f1f920edb7dcc4bc5f4f81b1b0255eb6fa87175","tid":903125,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T10:10:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leecheukyan.official/photos/a.437459349652687/2020669644664975/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fleecheukyan.official%2Fphotos%2Fa.437459349652687%2F2020669644664975%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=5l%2F0sjfIJ9RkNKjVOMlRBzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=a8777dd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/leecheukyan.official/photos/a.437459349652687/2020669644664975/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n李卓人 Lee Cheuk Yan<br />\n讚好此專頁 &middot; 19 小時 &middot; <br />\n <br />\n【背水一戰&mdash;&mdash;李卓人造勢大會】<br />\n林榮基、雄仔叔叔聯手撐場！ <br />\n<br />\n兩年前銅鑼灣書店事件，中國部門在香港越境擄人，震驚社會。事件中的主角林榮基先生，在經歷不能想像的荒誕之餘，卻提到得悉香港人為了他而上街聲討政權，就是對自己最大的鼓舞，留下名言：「香港人，無得退！」<br />\n<br />\n最近港台劇集《定風波》公映，再次提醒香港人高度自治的脆弱，我們能否在黑暗中守護這個城市，捍衛免於恐懼的自由，全在我們一念之間。星期五晚，我們請來劇中飾演林榮基先生的阮志雄（雄仔叔叔），與真．林榮基聯手撐場。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，無得退，就要背水一戰。<br />\n距離 11.25 投票日不足兩星期，<br />\n讓我們在榕樹頭下聚首，敲戰鼓，上戰場！<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<br />\n#林榮基：「這次西九補選，支持李卓人先生，有兩個理由，一個是他的資歷深，作為工黨領袖，三十多年，長期為工人服務，成績有目共睹；另一個就是現時立法會，16 票對 17 票，即是還欠一票，才有足夠的票數，為港人爭取應有的權益。<br />\n<br />\n這當中最迫切的，無疑是快將提上議程的 23 條*，如果不夠票數阻止，一旦通過，我們的言論自由將會失去。所以，支持李卓人先生，是不容置疑的。」<br />\n<br />\n#雄仔叔叔：「強權當道，反抗運動要寸土必爭。民間有各種作為，以喚發公民意志；議會亦要盡爭資源、空間配合。議會內的李卓人，在一般民主進程外，於勞工議題這重要板塊，都有力爭的經驗和能量。撐人哥！」<br />\n<br />\n按：鍾國斌的無約束力議案，最快 11 月 28 日在立法會大會辯論，一旦通過，將會為林鄭落實 23 條立法打下強心針。<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<br />\n【李卓人造勢大會】<br />\n日期｜11 月 16 日（星期五）<br />\n時間｜7.30-9.30PM<br />\n地點｜油麻地眾坊街榕樹頭公園<br />\n詳情 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PTCBCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PTCBCo&d=5l%2F0sjfIJ9RkNKjVOMlRBzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=c207d330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PTCBCo</a><br />\n<br />\n【寫在＜定風波＞公映前｜林榮基】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Pr92c6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Pr92c6&d=5l%2F0sjfIJ9RkNKjVOMlRBzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=b4cbc699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2Pr92c6</a><br />\n<br />\n#1125記得投票　#3號李卓人<br />\n#為下一代　#背水一戰<br />\n#選舉廣告<br />\n<br />\n【報名做義工】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/LeeCheukYan2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FLeeCheukYan2018&d=5l%2F0sjfIJ9RkNKjVOMlRBzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=f0f376b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/LeeCheukYan2018</a><br />\n【組隊入信箱】 <a href=\"http://goo.gl/54XeVT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F54XeVT&d=5l%2F0sjfIJ9RkNKjVOMlRBzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=405720cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goo.gl/54XeVT</a><br />\n【捐款支持李卓人】 <a href=\"http://leecheukyan.org/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fleecheukyan.org%2Fdonation&d=5l%2F0sjfIJ9RkNKjVOMlRBzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=4c858c8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">leecheukyan.org/donation</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/46342655_2020669651331641_3407725192649113600_n.png?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=de5ce08b79fcfe6c480eef5799631aeb&amp;oe=5C776F38\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F46342655_2020669651331641_3407725192649113600_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Dde5ce08b79fcfe6c480eef5799631aeb%26oe%3D5C776F38&h=10b75196&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b41b19156a4e7b871cc0da36e7fc27a27cb0862e","tid":903125,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:44:31.000Z","msg":"今晚"},{"pid":"bf8cd9199f294431169566fe4423eea3127e274b","tid":903125,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit